						<p><strong>Symptoms:</strong><br />
Wordpress detects a technical issue when upgrading to plugin version 2.1.8, e.g. when accessing the list of all installed plugins. Downgrade to version 2.1.6 works without any technical issue. Issue is related to new handling of robots.txt. In the system no robots.txt is installed at /usr/share/wordpress, which is not (and should not) be writable by www-data by design.</p>
<p><strong>Versions:</strong><br />
WordPress version 5.8.1 (from Debian distribution)<br />
Current plugin: W3 Total Cache (version 2.1.8)<br />
PHP version 7.4.24</p>
<p><strong>Error Details:</strong></p>
<pre><code>
An error of type E_ERROR was caused in line 242 of the file /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Util_WpFile.php. Error message: Uncaught W3TC\Util_WpFile_FilesystemOperationException in /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Util_WpFile.php:242
Stack trace:
#0 /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Generic_Environment.php(19): W3TC\Util_WpFile::file_exists()
#1 /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Root_Environment.php(28): W3TC\Generic_Environment-&gt;fix_on_wpadmin_request()
#2 /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Generic_Plugin_Admin.php(742): W3TC\Root_Environment-&gt;fix_in_wpadmin()
#3 /usr/share/wordpress/wp-includes/class-wp-hook.php(303): W3TC\Generic_Plugin_Admin-&gt;admin_notices()
#4 /usr/share/wordpress/wp-includes/class-wp-hook.php(327): WP_Hook-&gt;apply_filters()
#5 /usr/share/wordpress/wp-includes/plugin.php(470): WP_Hook-&gt;do_action()
#6 /usr/share/wordpress/wp-admin/admin-header.php(287): do_action()
#7 /usr/share/wordpress/wp-admin/index.php(115): require_once(&#039;/usr/share/word...&#039;)
#8 {main}
 thrown
</code></pre>
<p><strong>Solution:</strong><br />
Add try catch clause around Util_WpFile::file_exists statement in Generic_Environment.php:19</p>
<p><strong>Patch:</strong></p>
<pre><code>--- /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Generic_Environment.php.org	2021-09-30 11:01:21.007003048 +0200
+++ /var/lib/wordpress/wp-content/plugins/w3-total-cache/Generic_Environment.php	2021-09-30 11:04:30.142395960 +0200
@@ -15,7 +15,8 @@
 		$exs = new Util_Environment_Exceptions();
 		// create add-ins
 		$this-&gt;create_required_files( $config, $exs );
-
+
+		try {
 		if ( Util_WpFile::file_exists( Util_Environment::site_path() . &#039;robots.txt&#039; ) ) {
 			if ( $config-&gt;get_boolean( &#039;robots_block.enable&#039; ) ) {
 				$this-&gt;robots_rules_add( $config, $exs );
@@ -23,6 +24,9 @@
 				$this-&gt;robots_rules_remove( $exs );
 			}
 		}
+                } catch ( Util_WpFile_FilesystemOperationException $ex ) {
+                        $exs-&gt;push( $ex );
